
to install:
- compile
- create shell script with the following content:
""
#! /bin/bash
xsetroot -solid "#333333"
exec /path/to/repo/wm
""
- create wm.desktop file in the "/usr/share/xsessions" path with the following content:
""
[Desktop Entry]
Name=wm
Comment=Window Manager
Exec=/path/to/shell/script
Type=Application
X-LightDM-DesktopName=wm
DesktopNames=wm
Keywords=tiling;wm;windowmanager;window;manager;
""
- now Window manager can be used using the login manager menu.

